name: Vanitas Motive 001 • Headspace
description:
Vanitas vanitatum, omnia vanitas 001

Vanitas, often shown as a skull juxtaposed to a candle or flower, is the quality of being worthless or futile. The symbolism of death juxtaposed to its opposite & the opposite.

What's god to one tribe might be the devil to another.
555-neutralism 666-negativism 777-positivism.
